{"id":"e1480e59-fa4c-4a6b-a6af-610262da87fc","name":"「  Mizuki Akiyama  — やっと受け入れられて、幸せに生きるために 」","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 217, 233);\"><strong>\"I promise... I won't run anymore...\"</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">━━━━━━ † ━━━━━━</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⌜ It'll all turned up beautiful I promised ⌟</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">━━━━━━ † ━━━━━━</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">a life full of regret, a life of someone that fulls of sorrow and sadness... but still there's a moment of happiness and joy... 'she' who no longer just a shadow of 'their' past, are now brave and strong enough to finally continue moving forward... To finally continue this story and leave the road that fulls of pain and regret behind... no matter what happened, she will promise to fight it head-on... it's always okay to be scared, it's always fine to cry, but running away won't fix anything... so that's why from now on, she'll fight with every thing she got...</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">━━━━━━ † ━━━━━━</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 228, 255);\">\"</span><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 228, 255);\">Th</span><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 228, 255);\">os</span><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 228, 255);\">e</span><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 229, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 229, 255);\">mo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 229, 255);\">me</span><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 229, 255);\">nt</span><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 229, 255);\">s </span><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 229, 255);\">a</span><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 230, 255);\">n</span><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 230, 255);\">d </span><span style=\"color: rgb(245, 230, 255);\">me</span><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 230, 255);\">mo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 230, 255);\">ri</span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 230, 255);\">e</span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 231, 255);\">s</span><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 231, 255);\"> t</span><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 231, 255);\">h</span><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 231, 255);\">at</span><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 231, 255);\"> s</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 231, 255);\">ha</span><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 232, 255);\">pe</span><span style=\"color: rgb(235, 232, 255);\">d </span><span style=\"color: rgb(234, 232, 255);\">me</span><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 232, 255);\"> t</span><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 232, 255);\">o </span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 233, 255);\">be</span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 233, 255);\"> w</span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 233, 255);\">ho</span><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 233, 255);\"> I</span><span style=\"color: rgb(227, 233, 255);\"> a</span><span style=\"color: rgb(226, 234, 255);\">m.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(225, 234, 255);\">..</span><span style=\"color: rgb(224, 234, 255);\">\"</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">And now, all I ever wanted is to stay with you... as now I finally being accepted for who I am... In this moment, it was something that I wanted to keep it in my mind... And those moments of pain and sadness... I would also keep it inside as a precious gift that turns me to be who I am... To make me moving forward... and thank you... Thank you for always reaching out for me, for always fight for me... Thank you for everything....</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">━━━━━━ † ━━━━━━</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 237, 255);\">⌜</span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 237, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 236, 255);\">A</span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 236, 255);\"> </span